title: Bethlehem Catholic's football game Saturday moved up
text:
The Bethlehem Catholic football team will now host Pocono Mountain East Saturday at 11 a.m. (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By lehighvalleylive sports staff View/Post Comments 
Bethlehem Catholic 's football game Saturday, Oct. 17 against Pocono Mountain East has been moved up by two and a half hours. 
The Golden Hawks (5-1) will now host the Cardinals (2-4) at 11 a.m. at Bethlehem Area School District Stadium. 
The change was made to account for a potential Liberty soccer and/or field hockey game on Frank Banko Field early in the day because of an opponent's homecoming dance Saturday night.
